#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn45.34"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.34:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.34:0.2"
msgid "4. Paṭipattivagga "
msgstr "4. Practice "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.34:0.3"
msgid "34. Pāraṅgamasutta "
msgstr "34. Going to the Far Shore "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.34:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.34:1.2"
msgid "“Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā apārā pāraṃ gamanāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when these eight things are developed and cultivated they lead to going from the near shore to the far shore. "

msgctxt "sn45.34:1.3"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha? "
msgstr "What eight? "

msgctxt "sn45.34:1.4"
msgid "Seyyathidaṃ—sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "They are right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "

msgctxt "sn45.34:1.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā apārā pāraṃ gamanāya saṃvattantī”ti. "
msgstr "When these eight things are developed and cultivated they lead to going from the near shore to the far shore.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn45.34:2.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "sn45.34:2.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā: "
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn45.34:3.1"
msgid "“Appakā te manussesu, "
msgstr "“Few are those among humans "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:3.2"
msgid "ye janā pāragāmino; "
msgstr "who cross to the far shore. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:3.3"
msgid "Athāyaṃ itarā pajā, "
msgstr "The rest just run "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:3.4"
msgid "tīramevānudhāvati. "
msgstr "around on the near shore. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn45.34:4.1"
msgid "Ye ca kho sammadakkhāte, "
msgstr "When the teaching is well explained, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:4.2"
msgid "dhamme dhammānuvattino; "
msgstr "those who practice accordingly "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:4.3"
msgid "Te janā pāramessanti, "
msgstr "are the ones who will cross over "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:4.4"
msgid "maccudheyyaṃ suduttaraṃ. "
msgstr "Death’s domain so hard to pass. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn45.34:5.1"
msgid "Kaṇhaṃ dhammaṃ vippahāya, "
msgstr "Rid of dark qualities, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:5.2"
msgid "sukkaṃ bhāvetha paṇḍito; "
msgstr "an astute person should develop the bright. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:5.3"
msgid "Okā anokamāgamma, "
msgstr "Leaving home behind "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:5.4"
msgid "viveke yattha dūramaṃ. "
msgstr "for the seclusion so hard to enjoy, "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn45.34:6.1"
msgid "Tatrābhiratimiccheyya, "
msgstr "you should try to find delight there, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:6.2"
msgid "hitvā kāme akiñcano; "
msgstr "having left behind sensual pleasures. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:6.3"
msgid "Pariyodapeyya attānaṃ, "
msgstr "With no possessions, an astute person "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:6.4"
msgid "cittaklesehi paṇḍito. "
msgstr "should cleanse themselves of mental corruptions. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.1"
msgid "Yesaṃ sambodhiyaṅgesu, "
msgstr "And those whose minds are rightly developed "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.2"
msgid "sammā cittaṃ subhāvitaṃ; "
msgstr "in the awakening factors; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.3"
msgid "Ādānapaṭinissagge, "
msgstr "letting go of attachments, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.4"
msgid "anupādāya ye ratā; "
msgstr "they delight in not grasping. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.5"
msgid "Khīṇāsavā jutimanto, "
msgstr "With defilements ended, brilliant, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.6"
msgid "te loke parinibbutā”ti. "
msgstr "they are extinguished in this world.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.7"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
